msgctxt "Paragraph 1: Although Bill was gay, there were women he deeply cared for and considered an integral part of his life, especially after moving to California. I found no evidence from interviews or archival records ..."
msgid "In the California era, Bill was attracted to a few other women and with them he had the same intimate yet not intimate relationship he and I had as well."
msgstr ""

#: paragraph:1,sentence:9
msgctxt "Paragraph 1: Although Bill was gay, there were women he deeply cared for and considered an integral part of his life, especially after moving to California. I found no evidence from interviews or archival records ..."
