msgid "Also Bill was concerned that his homosexuality might reflect negatively on ACIM, a sacred trust in his eyes, and spending time with women could provide “cover.” Bill cannot easily be categorized in terms of his private life and his ambivalence challenged him, too."
msgstr ""

#: paragraph:2,sentence:11
